µBCµC0µF0µJLIn the second part of our exclusive interview, Peter Baustaedter explains why it made sense to rethink his character before his career really took off. He told us, if he'd stayed the same way as he was when he started out, he'd probably have failed to make it in Hollywood with his arrogant behaviour. The teamwork there is just completely different compared with the Amiga scene.
	
